 <notes>1.1.0:

Updates for better EndNote export support.

Thanks to Jean-Luc Aucouturier for contributions.


Basic usage of LibRIS:

require 'LibRIS.php';

// Parse and print
$ris = new LibRIS();
$ris-&gt;parseFile('./data.ris');
$ris-&gt;printRecords();

// Clone the above and write records.
$records = $ris-&gt;getRecords();
$rw = new RISWriter();
print $rw-&gt;writeRecords($records);

New in 1.1.0: Regex expanded to cover EndNote cases.

